:: Wolfgang ::

:: Wolfgang screams down the corridors of the Alliance base, the exit 
coming closer and closer.  In what seems to be an eternity, Wolfgang 
finnaly burts through, firing shots in a blaze of glory.  The veteran 
bot hadn't seen the sun, nor anything organic in ages.  He had missed 
the green grass and the tall trees he had so easily would of 
destroyed.  Although that side of him had not been as strong, it was 
still there.  Wolfgang proved this to himself by leveling a small 
patch of forest with a single blast of his rocket launcher. ::

Ahhhh....

:: It was good to be back ::
